metadata.name: Analog Edition – Page of Wands
metadata.description:
RELIX – Analog Edition

Page of Wands

Nascent fire nature. Inspiration often strikes like a bolt of lightning. Sometimes it touches the right surface and sparks a creative blaze; other times it’s as gone as fast as it appeared. Picture this potential in human form and you have your Page of Wands. When this card appears in a reading, search around for the person who stirs you to action, or look inward for the aspect of yourself that’s easily inspired.

Designed by Jiminie Ha & Jeremy Parker
Text by Michael George Land
More info at wolfhouse.art
